title: She Hates Her Nose And Wants To Get Surgery But Her Husband Says NO!
description:
She hates her nose and always has for quite some time. Starting in second grade after being made fun of.
She’s tolerated her most hated feature for all this time and thinks that she may have reached her breaking point.
